This paper is about face anti-spoofing, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method uses meta-learning, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions incorporating domain knowledge and regularization, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the experiments involve using public datasets, which are often used in multimedia (cs.MM) and computer security (cs.CR) research.
